metadata.name: Mechanical Monarch: A Steampunk Masterpiece
metadata.description:
The first 1/1 unique release of the Winged wonders is here.
.
Enter a world where the beauty of nature meets the power of steam. Behold the Mechanical Monarch, a 1/1 steampunk butterfly NFT created by the masterful artist, Oblivion Dope. With its intricate and mesmerising design, this NFT captures the essence of the steampunk aesthetic in a truly unique and captivating way.
.
The steampunk aesthetic is a unique and popular style that blends the intricate designs of the steam-powered age with the beauty of the natural world. It is characterised by its use of bronze and metallic colors, gears, and other mechanical elements, often combined with Victorian-era fashion and design. Steampunk is a celebration of creativity, innovation, and imagination, and has captured the hearts of people all over the world.
.
every week a new original butterfly design is coming out.
.
